#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:11
msgid "Ivan Bombs"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:13
msgid ""
"As with many other features of :game:`Yuri's Revenge`, the settings that "
"control Crazy Ivan Bombs are global so you cannot have multiple "
"variations of them with their own controls. With :game:`Ares` it is now "
"possible to create new Ivan Bomb-esque weapons -- new types of sticky "
"bomb with whatever settings you like."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:18
msgid ""
":game:`Ares` adds the Death Bombs feature, which was originally planned "
"to be in but were cut from the game before :game:`Red Alert 2` was "
"released. Death Bombs can rig victims with bombs that will not detonate "
"automatically, but remain active either until the unit dies to go off "
"then, or the owner manually detonates it, if allowed."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:24
msgid ""
":game:`Ares` now also supports shrapnel weapons, as long as they have a "
":tag:`CellSpread` of :value:`0.5` or more."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:32
msgid "General Bomb Settings"
msgstr ""

