"The warhead that will be used when the bomb detonates. Defaults to "
":tag:`[CombatDamage]IvanWarhead`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:44
msgid ":tagdef:`[Weapon]IvanBomb.Damage=integer`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:44
msgid ""
"The damage that will be dealt when the bomb detonates. Defaults to "
":tag:`[CombatDamage]IvanDamage`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:47
msgid ":tagdef:`[Weapon]IvanBomb.AttachSound=sound name`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:47
msgid ""
"The sound that will be played when the bomb is attached to a target. "
"Defaults to :tag:`[AudioVisual]BombAttachSound`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:54
msgid ":tagdef:`[Weapon]IvanBomb.TickingSound=sound name`"
msgstr ""

