msgid ":tagdef:`[Weapon]IvanBomb.DeathBombOnAllies=boolean`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/weapons/ivanbombs.rst:63
msgid ""
"Whether this bomb will be a death bomb instead of a timed bomb when "
"planted on allied objects. Defaults to :value:`no`."
msgstr ""

